## ğŸ’¡ Recommendations

### For Champions (15%)
âœ… **Exclusive benefits:** Early access to new products  
âœ… **Personal touch:** Thank you notes, birthday offers  
âœ… **Referral program:** Incentivize bringing new customers  

### For Loyal Customers (35%)
âœ… **Points program:** Reward repeat purchases  
âœ… **Bundling:** Offer product bundles at discount  
âœ… **Feedback:** Ask for reviews and testimonials  

### For At-Risk (28%)
âœ… **Re-engagement:** Email with special discount  
âœ… **Surveys:** Understand why they stopped buying  
âœ… **Limited time offers:** Create urgency to return  

### For Lost Customers (22%)
âœ… **Win-back campaign:** Aggressive discounts  
âœ… **New product showcase:** Show what they've missed  
âœ… **Easy return:** Remove friction from comeback  

